title: Sandisk 4GB MicroSDHC Memory Card with SD Adapter (BULK Packaging)
description: This SanDisk microSD High Capacity (microSDHC) flash card offers high storage capacity for storing essential digital content such as high quality photos, videos, music and more; optimal speed and performance for microSDHC compatible devices. SanDisk microSDHC 4GB card ships with Bonus MicroMate USB 2.0 SD/SDHC Reader, to ensure compatibility when downloading pictures or other digital content. Easily transfer files between your digital devices and computer.
